<C>__{rose}
<A>__{oh, stop it, mother. you'll give yourself a nosebleed. ruth pulls away from her, and crosses to the door, locking it. clack!}
<C>__{ruth}
<P>__{(wheeling on her)}
<A>__{rose, this is not a game! our situation is precarious. you know the money's gone!}
