<A>__{of course i know it's gone. you remind me every day!}
<C>__{ruth}
<A>__{your father left us nothing but a legacy of bad debts hidden by a good name. and that name is the only card we have to play. rose turns her around and grabs the corset strings again. ruth sucks in her waist and rose pulls.}
<C>__{ruth}
<A>__{i don't understand you. it is a fine match with hockley, and it will insure our survival.}
